                    <h4>Step 3: Add a Restriction</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Click <span class="badge bg-success"><i class="bi bi-plus"></i> Add Restriction</span></li>
                        <li>Enter the <strong>Property Name</strong> (e.g., "age", "email", "title")</li>
